trans-unit.source: The mission of grand Valley State University Art Gallery is to encourage appreciaton and understanding of art and its role in society through direct engagement with original works of art. The Art Gallery acquires, preserves, interprets, exhibits, and otherwise makes accessible works of art for the bemifit of a veriety of audienecs, in support of the interdisciplinary educational goals of university and for the benifit of the community at large.
